# Hash-ledgered repository: file BYTES are the commitment device
# (results/commitment_ledger.txt, run-ledger output_sha256). Git must never
# rewrite line endings on checkout — CRLF conversion on Windows changes every
# sha256 and reads as ledger corruption (caught by the Windows CI job).
* -text

# These source files intentionally retain their historical CRLF records.
datasets/pcso-lotto/*.csv whitespace=cr-at-eol
